title: Margo Martindale / Scoliosis
description: Sean covers both ends by mentally preparing for his upcoming colonoscopy. Sean and Dr. Wali talk about the human experience through time. A listener calls in about being born without a butthole. Margo Martindale bends over backwards to share her scoliosis story.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
